Primary job duties:

Reviewing new business initiatives and scoping any effect on existing transaction tax calculation processes and systems;
Providing transaction tax subject matter expertise to various business and IT organizations and various product groups;
Providing indirect tax calculation requirements for projects and business initiatives, including analyzing product type, taxability, rates, and invoicing for non-America’s countries;
Actively participating in projects throughout their lifecycle – from design, delivery, and ongoing maintenance;
Product taxability research across a wide range of categories for the non-Americas region;
Involvement in general non-Americans indirect tax research related to tax calculation and compliance, and tax collection responsibilities;
Actively participating throughout the indirect tax solutions lifecycle from planning through delivery (including directly or indirectly providing project management support) and ongoing support; and
Collaborate with business units to proactively identify and research non-Americas indirect tax planning opportunities.
